reviewText: It's a nice video, I just wished it was longer.  But any interview with Fillmore Slim is a great interview.

Could have been better video quality. More  like a home movie.  Shoddy for such a quality grand master a pimp like Fillmore Slim...expected better from Rosebudd. Orherwise great choppin up on the game from the true masters.

The one on one conversations were interesting but were hard to follow.  The "interview" process was too familiar and filled with too many inside jokes and references, overall watching the video felt like ease dropping.
This was a Real Documentary of the PIMP life a MUST SEE if your interested in the GAME... TRUE GAME WITH REAL PLAYAS
